collections.name: Ethereal Movements
collections.description:
Ethereal Movements is a mesmerizing NFT collection that transcends traditional digital art. Through dreamy cinematic clips, this collection captures the fluid elegance of high-fashion muses as they move through surreal, otherworldly environments. Each piece blends luxury aesthetics with otherworldly energy — from crystalline caves to golden-lit forests, reflective mirror realms and more.

Infused with depth, emotion, and the beauty of fleeting motion, Ethereal Movements invites collectors to experience art that feels alive, timeless, and untouchable. This collection embodies the essence of elegance in motion, offering both stillness and transformation in a single moment.

collections.name: TORI10000
collections.description:
TORI10000はトリの10000枚絵です。だいたい毎日一枚ずつ発表しています。すべてのトリにそれぞれの性格や暮らし、環境があってどの鳥もたくましく過ごしています。大きなトリ小さなトリ赤いトリに黄色いトリ青いトリ、どんなトリもみんなトリ。since 2025.3.20
TORI10000 is a collection of 10,000 bird illustrations. I release about one drawing per day. Each bird has its own personality, lifestyle, and environment, living strong and resilient. Big birds, small birds, red birds, yellow birds, blue birds—no matter the type, they are all birds. Since 2025.3.20.
